---
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Home
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Wikilear
hide_title: true
description: "Tutorial e suggerimenti su Google Workspace (Documenti Google, Fogli Google, Gmail, Drive, ecc.), Google Apps Script, Eleventy e Tailwind CSS"
subtitle:
image: /images/home.png
pagination:
  data: collections.feed
  size: 3
permalink: "{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}/page/{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}{% endif %}/"
paginationPrevText: "Articoli più recenti"
paginationNextText: "Articoli più vecchi"
paginationAnchor: "#all-articles"
feed: ""
schema:
  type: WebSite
---

{% block content %}
<div>
  <img
    src="/images/home.png"
    alt=""
    class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg mt-2 md:mt-4"
    data-lcp="high"
  />
<h1>Wikilear: tutorial, suggerimenti e trucchi alla portata di tutti</h1>
<p>Su Wikilear trovi guide e suggerimenti su come usare al meglio Google Workspace (Documenti Google, Fogli Google, Gmail, Google Drive, ecc.)
  e altri prodotti Google. Trovi anche utili tutorial su Google Apps Script, Eleventy e Tailwind CSS.</p>
</div>
<ul class="list-disc mx-4 p-4">
  <li><a href="#all-articles">Ultimi articoli</a></li>
  <li><a href="#topics">Argomenti principali</a></li>
</ul>
<article class="mx-1 sm:mx-2 md:mx-4">
  <div id="all-articles" class="heading my-2">
    {% set postListHeadline = 'Ultimi articoli pubblicati sul sito' %}
    {% set postListItems = pagination.items %} {% include
    "partials/post-list.njk" %} {% include "partials/pagination.njk" %}
  </div>
</article>
<nav
   class="heading my-8 mx-1 sm:mx-2 md:mx-4 text-center border rounded-lg shadow-lg font-bold"
>

  <h2 id="topics" class="mt-4 font-bold">Argomenti principali</h2>
  {% include 'components/card.njk' %}

</nav>

{% set cards = [
  { url: "/blog/", image: "/images/blog-post.svg", title: "Blog"},
  { url: "/tips-and-tricks/", image: "/images/undraw_team_up_ip2x.png", title: "Tips and tricks"},
  { url: "/termini-uso-privacy/", image: "/images/undraw_privacy_protection_nlwy.png", title: "Termini d'uso e privacy"},
  { url: "/tutorial/", image: "/images/tutorial.svg", title: "Tutorial"}
] %}

<nav id="sections" aria-label="Sezioni prinicipali del sito">
  <div class="mx-1 sm:mx-2 md:mx-4 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
    {% for card in cards %}
      <div
        class="w-full aspect-[4/3] flex flex-col border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-300 border rounded-lg shadow-lg"
      >
        <a href="{{ card.url }}">
          <div class="w-full h-12 flex flex-row justify-center items-center rounded-t-lg bg-gray-200 text-black font-semibold font text-xl">
            <p class="m-0">{{ card.title }}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-grow aspect-[5/4] items-center justify-center px-2">
            <img
              class="object-cover"
              src="{{ card.image }}"
              alt
              sizes="(min-width: 1280px) 258px, (min-width: 780px) 220px, (min-width: 680px) 244px, (min-width: 560px) calc(22vw + 99px), calc(100vw - 58px)"
            />
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</nav>

<article
  class="my-8 mx-1 sm:mx-2 md:mx-4 text-center border rounded-lg shadow-lg font-semibold"
>
  <details class="cursor-pointer" open>
    <summary id="tags" class="heading m-4 font-bold">Tutte le etichette</summary>
    {% include 'components/tagsList/tags-list.njk' %}
  </details>
</article>

<p>
  Wikilear è un progetto open source creato con
  <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/" aria-label="Eleventy (link al sito)">Eleventy</a> e
  <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/" aria-label="Tailwind CSS (link al sito)">Tailwind CSS,</a>
  e ospitato su <a href="https://www.netlify.com/">Netlify.</a> Trovi il codice sorgente su <a href="https://github.com/andrealeardini/wikilear" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub.</a> Wikilear è stato testato
  sulle ultime versioni dei più moderni browser: Chrome, Edge, Firefox, Opera e Safari. Se riscontri problemi grafici aggiorna il tuo browser.
</p>
{% endblock %}